data.description: Discover this appealing home at 8 Bowditch in Irvine, gracefully placed on a quiet cul-de-sac location in Northwood.  This single-story home is ready for new memories to be made, harmoniously blending relaxed comfort with the potential for your personal touch. Boasting an impressive 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath layout, expansive dining and living areas, and an enviable pool and private spa add a resort vibe to this lovely home! This gem truly encompasses the California Dream!  As you step through the front door, you're greeted by a large, open living with fireplace and dining area, complete with high vaulted ceilings that add an extra sense of space and light.  An open atrium in the center of the home offers private space to enjoy the outdoors.  The kitchen promises to be the heart of the home, an inviting start to any get-together.  Set on a 5,445 sq. ft. lot, this home delivers a sizeable, lushly landscaped yard perfect for family fun, gatherings or tranquil downtime.  This home also offers solar, 2-car garage, ample storage, NO HOA and central AC & heat providing year-round comfort.  This property's condition, though well-loved, offers perfect opportunities for upgrading to your unique tastes. Situated in the thriving Northwood community, this home presents accessibility to top-rated schools and parks.
